    "In the hitting point classification, the majority of the data was distributed in the \"Front\" category.",
    "This predominance led to no significant performance difference between the baseline and the top-performing models across two validation settings.",
    "Lastly, in the sound classification, varied performances were observed among the models.",
    "The Transformer model excelled in the 10-fold cross-validation, while the ConvLSTM and LSTM models displayed strong results in the LTO settings, particularly with LSTM leading in LTO for F1 score and accuracy.",
